name: 1-acylglycerol-3-phosphate O-acyltransferase
classes: Transferring groups other than aminoacyl groups
comment: Acyl-[acyl-carrier protein] can also act as an acyl donor. The animal enzyme is specific for the transfer of unsaturated fatty acyl groups.
